Events.Text: You remember that your friend recommended the Hyatt Hotel. Tell the assistant you've changed your mind and want to stay at Hyatt Hotel. [instruction 1 of 5]

Scenario.UserTask: Make a reservation at Old Town Inn from May 9th to 21st. Your name is Angela. Please request a balcony. It is ok if the room is not available - just say goodbye in this case.
Scenario.WizardTask: Help the user reserve a hotel room. (You can find the video tutorial under https://youtu.be/L7QpscLPTFM, in case you want to watch it again.)
